<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <meta name="renderer" content="webkit">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <title><%- title %></title>
    <%- include("./include/public") %>

    <style type="text/css">
        * {
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        /*导航*/
        #help {
            background-color: #000000;
            position: relative;
        }

        #help .navbar-default .navbar-nav > li > a {
            color: #FFF;
        }

        /*底部样式*/
        .footer_help {
            margin-top: 25px;
            background-color: #373737;
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 50px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        /*页面内容样式*/
        #ma {
            width: 104px;
            height: 34px;
            font-size: 22px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin-left: -31px;
        }

        .ma a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn_one {
            padding: 6px 15px;
            margin-left: -30px;
            border-radius: initial;
        }

        .col-sm-offset-5 {
            margin-left: 36.666667%;
        }

        .register_title {
            padding-left: 211px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
<%- include("./include/header") %>

<!-- 页面内容 -->
<div class="container" style="padding: 145px 0px;">
    <div class="col-sm-12" style="box-shadow: 0 5px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);float: left;padding: 100px 0;">
        <div class="col-sm-7" style="border-right: 1px solid #e5e4e4;">
            <div style="width: 60%;margin: auto;">

                <h3 class="register_title">忘 记 密 码</h3>

                <form class="form-horizontal" id="forgetPWDFrom" >
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-sm-4 control-label">手机号</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            <input name="userName" class="form-control"  placeholder="请输入手机号">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-sm-4 control-label">新密码</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="请输入新密码">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-sm-4 control-label">确认密码</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            <input type="password" name="confPassword" class="form-control" placeholder="请输入确认密码">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-sm-4 control-label">验证码</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-5">
                            <input name="captchaCode" class="form-control" placeholder="请输入验证码">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-3 ma" id="captchaDiv">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-sm-4 control-label">短信验证码</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-5">
                            <input name="SMSCode" class="form-control" placeholder="请输入短信验证码"
                                   style="border-radius: initial;">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-3">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary  btn_one">发送验证码</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-sm-offset-4 col-sm-8">
                            <button type="button" id="forgetPWDBtn" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">找回密码</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-5" style="padding: 21px 50px;">
            <p>已是安宝用户？<a href="public/login.ejs">立即登录</a></p>
            <p>您还可以关注安宝微信，随时掌控最新资讯！</p>
            <p><img src="/images/img/ab_gzh.png"/></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%- include("./include/buttom") %>
<script src="/javascripts/utils/popupUtils.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/utils/captchaUtils.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/utils/timer.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/function/forgetPassword.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
